replies.body:
Idk about Akali because her damage is just busted rn and she.. kinda needs a nerf,  agree on Zoe. Tho Zoe is a bit binary with "have cleanse/QSS or get oneshot as squishy", but she can play around it by poking and by having reliable damage from passive and W (tho both got nerfed hard recently which made her very weak).  

But I dont agree on Yasuo, like you said its hard to play safe with him, but if you do.. 
I think his kit would be very balanced if he was the glass cannon champ you described him as, but sadly one of his core items is {{item:3053}} with {{item:3046}} reducing your damage and Resolve giving him defense. People sometimes even go {{item:3046}} {{item:3053}} before finishing {{item:3031}}
